==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sopite
<hw>So"pite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sopitus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>sopire</ets> to put to sleep; akin to
<ets>sopor</ets> a sleeping draught, a heavy sleep.]</ety> <def>To lay
asleep; to put to sleep; to quiet.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The king's declaration for the <qex>sopiting</qex> of all Arminian
heresies.</q> <rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sopition</ent>⟦br⟧
